  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK288">
<l>aḷavaṟintār neñcat taṟampōla niṟkuṅ</l>
<l>kaḷavaṟintār neñciṟ karavu</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Deceit dwells in the mind of those who are conversant with fraud, even as virtue in the minds of those who are conversant with rectitude.</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
